(1) May purchase or lease a site for a facility established under
section 23-3501 and provide and equip any building deemed necessary to fulfill
the facility's mission;

(2) May accept property by gift, devise, bequest, or otherwise and
may carry out any conditions connected to the receipt of any gift, devise,
or bequest;

(5) Shall have
exclusive control of the expenditures of all money collected to the credit
of the fund for any such facility;

(8) Shall have the authority to pay all
bills and claims due and owing by the facility and the salaries of all employees
of such facility;
